#Importing to prevent problems with reading information
struct_mat_REP_final<-read.csv("./Analyses/structural_REP.csv")
struct_mat_REP_final<-struct_mat_REP_final[,-1]

values_to_plot<-c(0,1, 2,3)

CI_rep<-as.data.frame(expand.grid(values=values_to_plot, Te_Regime=c("SR4", "SR5"), Tu_Regime=c("SR1", "SR2"), Environment=c("N", "Cd")))

CI_rep$x<-mapvalues(CI_rep$values, c(0,1,2,3), c(0,8,8,0))
CI_rep$x_lower<-mapvalues(CI_rep$values, c(0,1,2,3), c(0,8,8,0))
CI_rep$x_upper<-mapvalues(CI_rep$values, c(0,1,2,3), c(0,8,8,0))

CI_rep$y<-sapply(c(1:dim(CI_rep)[1]), function(x){
  a<-subset(struct_mat_REP_final, Environment==CI_rep$Environment[x] &
  Te_Regime==CI_rep$Te_Regime[x] & Tu_Regime==CI_rep$Tu_Regime[x])
  
  if(CI_rep$values[x]==0 | CI_rep$values[x]==3){
         b<-0
  }else{
      if(CI_rep$values[x]==1){ 
          b<-a$a22_a12[1]*CI_rep$x[x]
        }else if(CI_rep$values[x]==2){
          b<-a$a21_a11[1]*CI_rep$x[x]
        }
      
    }
    b
  })


CI_rep$y_lower<-sapply(c(1:dim(CI_rep)[1]), function(x){
  a<-subset(struct_mat_REP_final, Environment==CI_rep$Environment[x] &
  Te_Regime==CI_rep$Te_Regime[x] & Tu_Regime==CI_rep$Tu_Regime[x])
  
  if(CI_rep$values[x]==0 | CI_rep$values[x]==3){
         b<-0
  }else{
    if(a$Environment[1]=="N"){
      if(a$Tu_Regime[1]=="SR2" & a$Te_Regime[1]=="SR5"){
        if(CI_rep$values[x]==1){ 
          b<-a$min_a22_a12[1]*CI_rep$x_lower[x]
        }else if(CI_rep$values[x]==2){
          b<-a$min_a21_a11[1]*CI_rep$x_lower[x]
        }
      
    }else{
      if(CI_rep$values[x]==1){ 
          b<-a$max_a22_a12[1]*CI_rep$x_lower[x]
        }else if(CI_rep$values[x]==2){
          b<-a$min_a21_a11[1]*CI_rep$x_lower[x]
        }}}
    else if(a$Environment[1]=="Cd"){
      if( a$Te_Regime[1]=="SR4"){
        if(CI_rep$values[x]==1){ 
          b<-a$min_a22_a12[1]*CI_rep$x_lower[x]
        }else if(CI_rep$values[x]==2){
          b<-a$max_a21_a11[1]*CI_rep$x_lower[x]
        }
      
    }else{
      if(CI_rep$values[x]==1){ 
          b<-a$max_a22_a12[1]*CI_rep$x_lower[x]
        }else if(CI_rep$values[x]==2){
          b<-a$max_a21_a11[1]*CI_rep$x_lower[x]
        }}
    }}
  b
})

CI_rep$y_upper<-sapply(c(1:dim(CI_rep)[1]), function(x){
  a<-subset(struct_mat_REP_final, Environment==CI_rep$Environment[x] &
  Te_Regime==CI_rep$Te_Regime[x] & Tu_Regime==CI_rep$Tu_Regime[x])
  
  if(CI_rep$values[x]==0 | CI_rep$values[x]==3){
         b<-0
  }else{
    if(a$Environment[1]=="N"){
      if(a$Tu_Regime[1]=="SR2" & a$Te_Regime[1]=="SR5"){
        if(CI_rep$values[x]==1){ 
          b<-a$max_a22_a12[1]*CI_rep$x_upper[x]
        }else if(CI_rep$values[x]==2){
          b<-a$max_a21_a11[1]*CI_rep$x_upper[x]
        }
      
    }else{
      if(CI_rep$values[x]==1){ 
          b<-a$min_a22_a12[1]*CI_rep$x_upper[x]
        }else if(CI_rep$values[x]==2){
          b<-a$max_a21_a11[1]*CI_rep$x_upper[x]
        }}}
    else if(a$Environment[1]=="Cd"){
      if( a$Te_Regime[1]=="SR4"){
        if(CI_rep$values[x]==1){ 
          b<-a$max_a22_a12[1]*CI_rep$x_upper[x]
        }else if(CI_rep$values[x]==2){
          b<-a$min_a21_a11[1]*CI_rep$x_upper[x]
        }
      
    }else{
      if(CI_rep$values[x]==1){ 
          b<-a$min_a22_a12[1]*CI_rep$x_upper[x]
        }else if(CI_rep$values[x]==2){
          b<-a$min_a21_a11[1]*CI_rep$x_upper[x]
        }}
    }}
  b
})

# Because in cadmium the boundaries change
CI_rep[which(CI_rep$Environment=="Cd" & CI_rep$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & CI_rep$Te_Regime=="SR5" & CI_rep$values==2), c("x_upper", "y_upper")]<-c(6/struct_mat_REP_final$min_a21_a11[which(struct_mat_REP_final$Environment=="Cd" & struct_mat_REP_final$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & struct_mat_REP_final$Te_Regime=="SR5")],6)

CI_rep[which(CI_rep$Environment=="Cd" & CI_rep$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & CI_rep$Te_Regime=="SR5" & CI_rep$values==2), c("x", "y")]<-c(6/struct_mat_REP_final$a21_a11[which(struct_mat_REP_final$Environment=="Cd" & struct_mat_REP_final$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & struct_mat_REP_final$Te_Regime=="SR5")],6)

CI_rep[which(CI_rep$Environment=="Cd" & CI_rep$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & CI_rep$Te_Regime=="SR5" & CI_rep$values==2), c("x_lower", "y_lower")]<-c(6/struct_mat_REP_final$max_a21_a11[which(struct_mat_REP_final$Environment=="Cd" & struct_mat_REP_final$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & struct_mat_REP_final$Te_Regime=="SR5")],6)


CI_rep[which(CI_rep$Environment=="Cd" & CI_rep$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & CI_rep$Te_Regime=="SR5" & CI_rep$values==1), c( "x_lower", "y_lower")]<-c(6/struct_mat_REP_final$max_a22_a12[which(struct_mat_REP_final$Environment=="Cd" & struct_mat_REP_final$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & struct_mat_REP_final$Te_Regime=="SR5")],6)

CI_rep[which(CI_rep$Environment=="Cd" & CI_rep$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & CI_rep$Te_Regime=="SR5" & CI_rep$values==1), c( "x","y")]<-c(6/struct_mat_REP_final$a22_a12[which(struct_mat_REP_final$Environment=="Cd" & struct_mat_REP_final$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & struct_mat_REP_final$Te_Regime=="SR5")],6)

CI_rep[which(CI_rep$Environment=="Cd" & CI_rep$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & CI_rep$Te_Regime=="SR5" & CI_rep$values==1), c( "x_upper","y_upper")]<-c(6/struct_mat_REP_final$min_a22_a12[which(struct_mat_REP_final$Environment=="Cd" & struct_mat_REP_final$Tu_Regime=="SR1" & struct_mat_REP_final$Te_Regime=="SR5")],6)


CI_rep[which(CI_rep$Environment=="Cd" & CI_rep$Tu_Regime=="SR2" & CI_rep$Te_Regime=="SR5" & CI_rep$values==1), c( "x_upper","y_upper")]<-c(6/struct_mat_REP_final$min_a21_a11[which(struct_mat_REP_final$Environment=="Cd" & struct_mat_REP_final$Tu_Regime=="SR2" & struct_mat_REP_final$Te_Regime=="SR5")],-2)

CI_rep[which(CI_rep$Environment=="Cd" & CI_rep$Tu_Regime=="SR2" & CI_rep$Te_Regime=="SR5" & CI_rep$values==3), c( "x_upper","y_upper")]<-c(6/struct_mat_REP_final$min_a22_a12[which(struct_mat_REP_final$Environment=="Cd" & struct_mat_REP_final$Tu_Regime=="SR2" & struct_mat_REP_final$Te_Regime=="SR5")],3)

CI_rep[which(CI_rep$Environment=="Cd" & CI_rep$Tu_Regime=="SR2" & CI_rep$Te_Regime=="SR5" & CI_rep$values==2), c( "x_upper","y_upper")]<-c(8,8)
Final figure
normal_feas<-ggplot(subset(struct_mat_REP_final, Environment=="N"), aes(x=Tu_lambda, y=Te_lambda, colour=interaction(Tu_Regime, Te_Regime)))+
  facet_grid(Tu_Regime~ Te_Regime, labeller=labeller(Tu_Regime=regimeTu, Te_Regime=regimeTe) )+
  geom_polygon(data=subset(CI_rep,Environment=="N"),aes(x=x_upper, y=y_upper), fill="tan1", alpha=0.35, colour="tan1", linetype="dashed", linewidth=1.2)+
  geom_polygon(data=subset(CI_rep,Environment=="N"),aes(x=x, y=y), fill="grey60", alpha=0.75, colour="black", linewidth=1.3)+
  geom_polygon(data=subset(CI_rep,Environment=="N"),aes(x=x_lower, y=y_lower), fill="lightskyblue1", alpha=0.9, col="lightskyblue1", linetype="dashed", linewidth=1.2)+
  geom_point(colour="black")+
  geom_segment(data=subset(struct_mat_REP_final, Environment=="N" ), aes(xend=Tu_lambda, yend=Te_lambda,x=0, y=0),  arrow=arrow(length = unit(0.3, "cm")), colour="black", linewidth=1.1)+
  geom_segment(data=subset(struct_mat_REP_final, Environment=="N" ), aes(xend=Tu_lambda_lower, yend=Te_lambda_lower,x=0, y=0),  colour="grey42", linetype="dashed", linewidth=1.1)+
  geom_segment(data=subset(struct_mat_REP_final, Environment=="N" ), aes(xend=Tu_lambda_upper, yend=Te_lambda_upper,x=0, y=0), colour="grey42", linetype="dashed", linewidth=1.1)+
  theme_bw()+
  theme_ines+
   ylab(c("Intrinsic growth rate T. evansi"))+
  xlab(c("Intrinsic growth rate T. urticae"))+
  theme(legend.position = "none")+
  #ylim(c(0,8))+
  #xlim(c(0,5))+
  coord_cartesian(xlim =c(0.1,2.8), ylim=c(0.1,6), expand = TRUE)
normal_feas
